<td class="navbox-group" style=";;"><a href="/wiki/Ethnic_groups_in_the_United_States" title="Ethnic groups in the United States">Race,<br />
ethnicity,<br />
and ancestry</a></td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;text-align:left;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<div>
<p><a href="/wiki/Category:Ethnic_groups_in_the_United_States" title="Category:Ethnic groups in the United States">Ethnic groups in the United States</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Category:American_people_by_ethnic_or_national_origin" title="Category:American people by ethnic or national origin">American people by ethnic or national origin</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Category:History_of_the_United_States_by_ethnic_group" title="Category:History of the United States by ethnic group">History of the United States by ethnic group</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Category:American_culture_by_ethnicity" title="Category:American culture by ethnicity">American culture by ethnicity</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Race_and_ethnicity_in_the_United_States_Census" title="Race and ethnicity in the United States Census">Race and ethnicity in the United States Census</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ethnic_groups_in_the_United_States" title="Ethnic groups in the United States">Ethnic groups in the United States</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Maps_of_American_ancestries" title="Maps of American ancestries">Maps&#160;of American&#160;ancestries</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/United_States_Census,_2000" title="United States Census, 2000" class="mw-redirect">2000&#160;Census</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Race_and_ethnicity_(EEO)" title="Race and ethnicity (EEO)">Race/ethnicity by EEOC</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Racism_in_the_United_States" title="Racism in the United States">Racism</a></p>
</div>
<p>Major examples: <a href="/wiki/Arab_Americans" title="Arab Americans" class="mw-redirect">Arab and Middle Eastern Americans</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Racial_and_ethnic_demographics_of_the_United_States#Black_Americans" title="Racial and ethnic demographics of the United States" class="mw-redirect">Black Americans</a> (<a href="/wiki/African_American" title="African American">African Americans</a>, <a href="/wiki/Black_Americans_of_African_Immigrant_origin" title="Black Americans of African Immigrant origin" class="mw-redirect">African immigrants</a>, <a href="/wiki/Afro-Caribbean_American" title="Afro-Caribbean American">Afro-Caribbeans</a>, etc)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Asian_American" title="Asian American">Asian Americans</a> (<a href="/wiki/Chinese_American" title="Chinese American">Chinese Americans</a>, <a href="/wiki/Filipino_American" title="Filipino American">Filipino Americans</a>, <a href="/wiki/Indian_American" title="Indian American">Indian Americans</a>, <a href="/wiki/Japanese_American" title="Japanese American">Japanese Americans</a>, <a href="/wiki/Pacific_Islander_American" title="Pacific Islander American">Pacific Islander Americans</a>, etc.) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/European_American" title="European American">European Americans</a> ("<a href="/wiki/White_American" title="White American">White Americans</a>")<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Hispanic_and_Latino_American" title="Hispanic and Latino American" class="mw-redirect">Hispanic and Latino Americans</a> (<a href="/wiki/Mexican_American" title="Mexican American">Mexican Americans</a>, <a href="/wiki/Puerto_Ricans_in_the_United_States" title="Puerto Ricans in the United States">Puerto Ricans in the United States</a>, <a href="/wiki/Cuban_American" title="Cuban American">Cuban Americans</a>, etc.)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jewish_Americans" title="Jewish Americans" class="mw-redirect">Jewish Americans</a> (<a href="/wiki/Jewish_ethnic_divisions" title="Jewish ethnic divisions">by ethnic origin</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Multiracial_American" title="Multiracial American">Multiracial Americans</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Native_Americans_in_the_United_States" title="Native Americans in the United States">Native&#160;Americans</a> (<a href="/wiki/Alaska_Natives" title="Alaska Natives">Alaska Natives</a>, <a href="/wiki/Native_Hawaiians" title="Native Hawaiians">Native Hawaiians</a>, etc.)</p>
</div>
