iki/Red_states_and_blue_states" title="Red states and blue states">Red states and blue states</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Uncle_Sam" title="Uncle Sam">Uncle Sam</a></span></div>
