<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<div>
<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Antigua_and_Barbuda&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Antigua and Barbuda (page does not exist)">Antigua and Barbuda</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_the_Bahamas&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in the Bahamas (page does not exist)">Bahamas</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Barbados&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Barbados (page does not exist)">Barbados</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Belize&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Belize (page does not exist)">Belize</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Poverty_in_Canada" title="Poverty in Canada">Canada</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Costa_Rica&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Costa Rica (page does not exist)">Costa Rica</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Cuba&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Cuba (page does not exist)">Cuba</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Dominica&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Dominica (page does not exist)">Dominica</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_the_Dominican_Republic&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in the Dominican Republic (page does not exist)">Dominican Republic</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_El_Salvador&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in El Salvador (page does not exist)">El Salvador</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Grenada&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Grenada (page does not exist)">Grenada</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Guatemala&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Guatemala (page does not exist)">Guatemala</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Haiti&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Haiti (page does not exist)">Haiti</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Honduras&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Honduras (page does not exist)">Honduras</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Jamaica&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Jamaica (page does not exist)">Jamaica</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Mexico&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Mexico (page does not exist)">Mexico</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Nicaragua&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Nicaragua (page does not exist)">Nicaragua</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Panama&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Panama (page does not exist)">Panama</a><sup><small>1</small></sup>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Poverty_in_Saint_Kitts_and_Nevis&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Poverty in Saint Kitts and Nevis (page does not exist)">Saint Kitts and Nevis</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span styl